### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### Create Email Notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "EMAIL",
  "recipient": "test@example.com",
  "subject": "Welcome Email",
  "content": "Thank you for registering! Your account is ready."
}

### Create SMS Notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "SMS",
  "recipient": "+1234567890",
   "subject": "Welcome SMS",
  "content": "Your verification code: 123456"
}

### Get Notification by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/2

### Get Recent Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/recent

### Update Notification (Full)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "subject": "Updated Subject",
  "content": "updated content"
}

### Update Notification (Partial - Subject Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "subject": "Only subject updated"
}

### Update Notification (Partial - Content Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Only content updated"
}

### Delete Notification
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notifications/2

### === ERROR TESTS ===

### Validation Error - Missing Required Fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

